					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 美國伊利諾州一名男子為了不讓家中貓咪獨守家門，決定與牠們一同環遊世界，他自20 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/03/%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e8%8a%b1%e5%b0%87%e8%bf%91%e7%99%be%e8%90%ac%e5%b8%b6%e6%84%9b%e8%b2%93%e5%87%ba%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a%ef%bc%81%e7%90%86%e7%94%b1%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b/">男子花將近百萬帶愛貓出國旅遊！理由曝光讓網友感到震驚 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/evenson-calder-Qc1m43DT6co-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>美國伊利諾州一名男子為了不讓家中貓咪獨守家門，決定與牠們一同環遊世界，他自2023年飼養了兩隻小貓後，便放下以往獨自出國旅行的習慣，轉而投入「帶貓旅行」的生活模式，至今為止已花費將近百萬台幣，只為讓愛貓們成為自己旅途中不可或缺的同伴。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這名男子原本是一位熱愛旅遊的背包客，幾乎每年都會安排多次跨國旅行，但在2023年家中迎來兩隻新成員後，他因為無法放心將小貓們獨留家中，也不想放棄自己旅遊的興趣，於是開始訓練小貓適應外出環境。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1627" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1627&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-221279" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/iren-liao-tZmSDZ6LsI8-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=110%2C146&amp;ssl=1 110w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">男子發現愛貓初次搭飛機意外淡定，這讓他心裡萌生起帶愛貓環遊世界的計畫<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>男子先讓愛貓們漸漸習慣人群、機場與陌生的聲音，並特別挑選寵物友善的航班與住宿設施，幸好小貓們在初次搭機時表現出意外的淡定，這讓男子深受鼓舞，下定決心展開一項「帶貓咪環遊世界」的旅遊計畫。&nbsp;</p>



<p>隨著時間流逝，兩隻貓早已適應了飛行與各國環境，也不再對陌生人感到恐懼，後來男子又陸續收養了新成員，成一支迷你寵物旅遊團，雖然每次帶貓旅行的開銷都不小，平均需額外支付約3萬元的機票與用品費，但男子認為能與愛貓一同看世界、一起留下回憶，這筆花費再多也值得。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/03/%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e8%8a%b1%e5%b0%87%e8%bf%91%e7%99%be%e8%90%ac%e5%b8%b6%e6%84%9b%e8%b2%93%e5%87%ba%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a%ef%bc%81%e7%90%86%e7%94%b1%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b/">男子花將近百萬帶愛貓出國旅遊！理由曝光讓網友感到震驚 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
