		<title>狗狗也會挑人黏 ? 其實他更愛有「這種」特質的人!</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/03/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b9%9f%e6%9c%83%e6%8c%91%e4%ba%ba%e9%bb%8f-%e5%85%b6%e5%af%a6%e4%bb%96%e6%9b%b4%e6%84%9b%e6%9c%89%e3%80%8c%e9%80%99%e7%a8%ae%e3%80%8d%e7%89%b9%e8%b3%aa%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%ba/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 06:11:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
